		<div class="story-heads">
		<h1>Allegra Goodman, Ej Dickson, Chris Jennings, and more: 22 new books out today!</h1>
			</div>
	</div>
										<div class="byline-date">
					<span class="byline"><a href="https://lithub.com/author/juliahass/"  title="Julia Hass">Julia Hass</a></span>
					<span class="hr"></span>
					<span class="date">February 10, 2026</span>
				</div>
						<div class="story-body">
								<p style="text-align: left;">Five more weeks of winter, says Punxsutawney Phil, but who&#8217;s counting? As the week eases into Valentine&#8217;s Day, I can&#8217;t say there&#8217;s a huge selection of romance in this week&#8217;s batch, but romance is in the eyes of the beholder. If you find treatises on &#8220;bad mothers,&#8221; or young Tennyson, or mathematical theories of the mind romantic, then disregard the above. No matter what, you will find them sharp and eye-opening. In terms of fiction, we welcome a new novel by Allegra Goodman, a debut by Kenan Orhan, and the delightfully titled <em>Murder Bimbo</em> by Rebecca Novak. Happy reading, everyone!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">*</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="264400" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/lit-hubs-most-anticipated-books-of-2026/allegra-goodman-this-is-not-about-us/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Allegra-Goodman-This-is-Not-About-Us.jpg" data-orig-size="987,1500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Allegra Goodman, This is Not About Us" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Allegra-Goodman-This-is-Not-About-Us-197x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Allegra-Goodman-This-is-Not-About-Us-674x1024.jpg" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-264400" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Allegra-Goodman-This-is-Not-About-Us-197x300.jpg" alt="Allegra Goodman, This is Not About Us" width="197" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Allegra-Goodman-This-is-Not-About-Us-197x300.jpg 197w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Allegra-Goodman-This-is-Not-About-Us-674x1024.jpg 674w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Allegra-Goodman-This-is-Not-About-Us-768x1167.jpg 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Allegra-Goodman-This-is-Not-About-Us-39x60.jpg 39w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Allegra-Goodman-This-is-Not-About-Us-33x50.jpg 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Allegra-Goodman-This-is-Not-About-Us.jpg 987w" sizes="(max-width: 197px) 100vw, 197px" /></p>
